# UI Implementation Rules

- Reuse existing UI components from `/src/components/`; these are the primitives we can build with.
- Create new components by composing existing ones if you can't find any that solve the problem.
- Ask the human how they want to proceed when there are missing components or designs.
- Use the `useConfig` hook for any configuration-driven UI behavior.
- Keep component files focused; one component per file.
